Other important globals: `StatutTrello`, `GanttModel`, `GanttTrello`, `AgentMemory`, `MemoryUI`, `AgentBlocks`, `CardHistory`, `UserProfile`, `People`, `PriorityMatrix`, `GoalsTrello` / `GoalsUI`, `OutlookSync` / `OutlookAuth` / `OutlookGraph`.

## PluginData budget

Trello allows **4096 chars per scope/visibility (all keys combined)**.

- `card/private` is shared by `cardAgentChat`, `cardEditHistory`, etc. — keep chat/history slim.
- Prefer board/shared for catalogs; member/private for provider + profile + people.

## Conventions when editing

1. Match existing IIFE + `'use strict'` + `global.Foo = …` style.
2. Update the file’s header TOC when adding a major section.
3. After logic changes under `components/`, run `npm run test:unit` (or `npm test`).
4. Do not introduce a bundler, TypeScript, or new framework without an explicit request.
5. Agent-visible copy: no em dashes; FR punctuation rules live in `PriorityAgent` polish helpers.
